#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-11-minimal-zsh-plugins.rst:8
msgid ""
"Zsh での最小構成の Zsh プラグイン導入方法を紹介します。 "
"本記事では、プラグインマネージャを使わずに手動で導入し、必須プラグインの構成を整理します。"
msgstr ""
"We will introduce how to install the Zsh plugin with a minimal configuration"
" using Zsh. In this article, we will install it manually without using the "
"plugin manager and organize the configuration of the required plugins."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-11-minimal-zsh-plugins.rst:16
msgid "概要"
msgstr "overview"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-11-minimal-zsh-plugins.rst:17
msgid "Starship を事前に導入済み　⇒ :doc:`2025-05-03-initail-setup-zsh`"
msgstr ""
"Starship has been installed in advance ⇒ :doc:`2025-05-03-initail-setup-zsh`"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-11-minimal-zsh-plugins.rst:18
msgid "最低限のプラグインのみ"
msgstr "Only minimal plugins"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-11-minimal-zsh-plugins.rst:19
msgid "`.zshrc` だけで完結"
msgstr "Complete with just `.zshrc`"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-11-minimal-zsh-plugins.rst:22
msgid "対象プラグイン"
msgstr "Target plugin"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-11-minimal-zsh-plugins.rst:24
msgid "以下はすべて **Starship と競合しない** ものです。"
msgstr "All of the following do not conflict with Starship."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-11-minimal-zsh-plugins.rst:26
msgid "``zsh-autosuggestions``：過去の履歴などから自動補完を提示"
msgstr ""
"``zsh-autosuggestions``: Suggest auto-completion from past history etc."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-11-minimal-zsh-plugins.rst:27
msgid "``zsh-syntax-highlighting``：入力中のコマンド構文を色分け"
msgstr ""
"``zsh-syntax-highlighting``: Color-code the command syntax you are typing"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-11-minimal-zsh-plugins.rst:28
msgid "``zsh-completions``：公式以外の補完も含めて強化"
msgstr "``zsh-completions``: Enhanced to include non-official completions"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-11-minimal-zsh-plugins.rst:31
msgid "プラグインの手動導入"
msgstr "Manual installation of plugins"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-11-minimal-zsh-plugins.rst:33
msgid "以下のコードを ``.zshrc`` に記述することで、**初回のみ clone し、2回目以降はスキップ** できます。"
msgstr ""
"By writing the following code in ``.zshrc``, you can **clone only the first "
"time and skip the second and subsequent times**."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-11-minimal-zsh-plugins.rst:59
msgid "Starship との順序関係"
msgstr "Order relationship with Starship"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-11-minimal-zsh-plugins.rst:61
msgid "Starship を使っている場合、``.zshrc`` の先頭で初期化する必要があります。"
msgstr ""
"If you are using Starship, you will need to initialize it at the top of your"
" ``.zshrc``."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-11-minimal-zsh-plugins.rst:72
msgid "dotfiles管理として、Git 管理から除外する"
msgstr "Exclude from Git management as dotfiles management"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-11-minimal-zsh-plugins.rst:74
msgid "プラグインは clone すれば再取得できるため、Git 管理から除外すべきです。"
msgstr ""
"Plugins can be re-obtained by cloning, so they should be excluded from Git "
"management."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-11-minimal-zsh-plugins.rst:82
msgid "まとめ"
msgstr "summary"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-11-minimal-zsh-plugins.rst:84
msgid "zsh の最小構成のプラグイン導入により補完機能が充実して、コマンドの入力が効率化されます。"
msgstr ""
"Introducing a minimal plugin for zsh enriches the completion functions and "
"makes command entry more efficient."

